  <entry xml:base="http://www.miriamsuzanne.com/feed.atom">
    <title type="text">America Heard: Transitions</title>
    <id>http://www.miriamsuzanne.com/2017/01/19/america-heard</id>
    <updated>2017-01-19T00:00:00Z</updated>
    <link href="http://www.miriamsuzanne.com/2017/01/19/america-heard" />
    <author>
      <name>Miriam Suzanne</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;My friend &lt;a class=&quot;reference external&quot; href=&quot;http://maureenleemaloney.com/&quot;&gt;Maureen Maloney&lt;/a&gt; asked to document
my reaction to the 2016 election,
as part of the &lt;a class=&quot;reference external&quot; href=&quot;https://americaheard.com/&quot;&gt;America Heard&lt;/a&gt; film&amp;nbsp;series:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our goal is to feature at least one film
from each of the 435 congressional districts
and show the diversity of political perspectives
throughout the United&amp;nbsp;States.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;attribution&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;a class=&quot;reference external&quot; href=&quot;https://americaheard.com/&quot;&gt;America&amp;nbsp;Heard&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working with Dana Forsberg and Katie Cook,
we put together this short documentary —
talking about trans rights,
and completing one step of my legal name change.
Thanks to &lt;a class=&quot;reference external&quot; href=&quot;http://teacupgorilla.com/&quot;&gt;Teacup Gorilla&lt;/a&gt; and Erin Rollman
for joining in the&amp;nbsp;fun!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;div data-gallery=&quot;video&quot; data-size=&quot;full&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;video-wrap&quot;&gt;
  &lt;iframe src=&quot;https://player.vimeo.com/video/198228746?color=c30062&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; height=&quot;450&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
